  "translations": {
    "en": {
      "likert_1": "Very Inaccurate",
      "likert_2": "Moderately Inaccurate",
      "likert_3": "Neither Accurate Nor Inaccurate",
      "likert_4": "Moderately Accurate",
      "likert_5": "Very Accurate",
      "question_head": "<h3>How Accurately Can You Describe Yourself?</h3>\nDescribe yourself as you generally are now, not as you wish to be in the future. Describe yourself as you honestly see yourself, in relation to other people you know of the same sex as you are, and roughly your same age. So that you can describe yourself in an honest manner, your responses will be kept in absolute confidence. Indicate how accurately this statement describes you.",
      "ipip_hexaco_001": "Accept people as they are.",
      "ipip_hexaco_002": "Am quick to judge others.",
      "ipip_hexaco_003": "Become frustrated and angry with people when they don't live up to my expectations.",
      "ipip_hexaco_004": "Criticize others' shortcomings.",
      "ipip_hexaco_005": "Find fault with everything.",
      "ipip_hexaco_006": "Have a good word for everyone.",
      "ipip_hexaco_007": "Have a sharp tongue.",
      "ipip_hexaco_008": "Rarely complain.",
      "ipip_hexaco_009": "Speak ill of others.",
      "ipip_hexaco_010": "Take things as they come.",
      "ipip_hexaco_011": "Act impulsively when something is bothering me.",
      "ipip_hexaco_012": "Avoid mistakes.",
      "ipip_hexaco_013": "Do things according to a plan.",
      "ipip_hexaco_014": "Do things without thinking of the consequences.",
      "ipip_hexaco_015": "Don't know why I do some of the things I do.",
      "ipip_hexaco_016": "Jump into things without thinking.",
      "ipip_hexaco_017": "Make a fool of myself.",
      "ipip_hexaco_018": "Make careless mistakes.",
      "ipip_hexaco_019": "Make plans and stick to them.",
      "ipip_hexaco_020": "Make rash decisions.",
      "ipip_hexaco_021": "Act like different people in different situations.",
      "ipip_hexaco_022": "Don't pretend to be more than I am.",
      "ipip_hexaco_023": "Find it necessary to please the people who have power.",
      "ipip_hexaco_024": "Let people push me around to help them feel important.",
      "ipip_hexaco_025": "Play a role in order to impress people.",
      "ipip_hexaco_026": "Pretend to be concerned for others.",
      "ipip_hexaco_027": "Put on a show to impress people.",
      "ipip_hexaco_028": "Switch my loyalties when I feel like it.",
      "ipip_hexaco_029": "Tell other people what they want to hear so that they will do what I want them to do.",
      "ipip_hexaco_030": "Use flattery to get ahead.",
      "ipip_hexaco_031": "Adjust easily.",
      "ipip_hexaco_032": "Am annoyed by others' mistakes.",
      "ipip_hexaco_033": "Am good at taking advice.",
      "ipip_hexaco_034": "Am hard to convince.",
      "ipip_hexaco_035": "Am hard to reason with.",
      "ipip_hexaco_036": "Am hard to satisfy.",
      "ipip_hexaco_037": "Can't stand being contradicted.",
      "ipip_hexaco_038": "Get upset if others change the way that I have arranged things.",
      "ipip_hexaco_039": "React strongly to criticism.",
      "ipip_hexaco_040": "When interacting with a group of people, am often bothered by at least one of them.",
      "ipip_hexaco_041": "Admire a really clever scam.",
      "ipip_hexaco_042": "Cheat on people who have trusted me.",
      "ipip_hexaco_043": "Cheat to get ahead.",
      "ipip_hexaco_044": "Return extra change when a cashier makes a mistake.",
